{"segment_id": "shijing__xiaoya-gufeng-001__001__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "xiaoya-gufeng-001", "source_id": "xiaoya-gufeng-001__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 1, "canonical_ref": "詩經·小雅·谷風之什·001.1", "text_original": "習習谷風，維風及雨。\n將恐將懼，維予與女。\n將安將樂，女轉棄予。", "text_normalized": "習習谷風，維風及雨。\n將恐將懼，維予與女。\n將安將樂，女轉棄予。", "notes": "谷風 Chinese stanza 1."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__xiaoya-gufeng-001__002__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "xiaoya-gufeng-001", "source_id": "xiaoya-gufeng-001__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 2, "canonical_ref": "詩經·小雅·谷風之什·001.2", "text_original": "習習谷風，維風及頹。\n將恐將懼，寘予于懷。\n將安將樂，棄予如遺。", "text_normalized": "習習谷風，維風及頹。\n將恐將懼，寘予于懷。\n將安將樂，棄予如遺。", "notes": "谷風 Chinese stanza 2."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__xiaoya-gufeng-001__003__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "xiaoya-gufeng-001", "source_id": "xiaoya-gufeng-001__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 3, "canonical_ref": "詩經·小雅·谷風之什·001.3", "text_original": "習習谷風，維山崔嵬。\n無草不死，無木不萎。\n忘我大德，思我小怨。", "text_normalized": "習習谷風，維山崔嵬。\n無草不死，無木不萎。\n忘我大德，思我小怨。", "notes": "谷風 Chinese stanza 3."}
